Package: csotoolkit
Type: Package
Title: Shared Helpers for UNICEF DW-Production Database Managers
Version: 0.4.3
Date: 2026-05-28
Authors@R: c(
    person("Joao Pedro", "Azevedo", email = "jazevedo@unicef.org",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = "UNICEF Chief Statistician"),
    person("UNICEF Data & Analytics", role = "cph")
  )
Description: Uniform IO, cached API access, mode-aware path routing, and
    version-drift detection helpers for UNICEF Data & Analytics database
    managers, reviewers, and ingestors working with the DW-Production
    indicator data warehouse. Designed for vendoring (copy into 00_functions/)
    rather than CRAN-style installation, to honour vintage permanence and
    AppLocker constraints on UNICEF laptops.
